title.children: Daniel Andrews steps down as an undefeated leader. What were his legacies?

image.altText: Australia's parliament house on a clear sunny day with tick and cross checkboxes illustrated over the top.

props.synopsis: Despite being on the cusp of early voting for the Voice to Parliament referendum, many still have questions about the proposal, one of them being; why can't it just be legislated?

title.children: You Ask We Answer: Why has the government opted for a referendum on the Voice to Parliament rather than legislation?

image.altText: Man wearing a suit and black jacket standing next to a wall.

title.children: Fentanyl has wreaked havoc in the United States. These experts worry Victoria could be next

image.altText: Jim Chalmers stands in a courtyard at parliament house.

title.children: The Albanese government missed a huge opportunity for a historic new target this week

image.altText: Emmanuel Macron stands behind a door frowning in the distance.

title.children: 'If others challenge him, he will take them on': French President Emmanuel Macron's unshakable self-belief

image.altText: Commander of the Russian Black Sea Fleet Vice-Admiral Viktor Sokolov.

image.altText: A woman carrying a jacket and another woman walk alongside building.

image.altText: Handcuffed prisoner being led in corridor by warden.

image.altText: Four women stand on a lawn and hug

image.altText: Sheila Chepkirui and Tigist Assefa hold an adidas shoe

image.altText: An NRL player stand allow, yelling wiht excitement, puffing his chest.

image.altText: A car submerged in the ocean with just the roof showing

image.altText: A woman with short blonde hair and glasses walking outside Adelaide's Magistrates Court.

image.altText: Mundine stands behind a lectern, a large blue screen with the press club logo behind him.

image.altText: An Indigenous woman leaning up against a door frame with a smile, wearing a pattern t-shirt

image.altText: Victorian Premier Daniel Andrews punches the air, surrounded by his wife and two adult children.

image.altText: Daniel Andrews makes a hand gesture at a press conference. He is outdoors

image.altText: plan landing on tarmac with wheel down and cityscape in the background

image.altText: A man wearing sunglasses and a racecar driver's outfit.

image.altText: Penguins on a iceberg.
